<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>tread on someone’s heels • tread on someone’s toes </xh5><p> <i>tread on someone’s heels—</i>follow a person very closely: We were walking up the hill, and our pace was much the same—I was <u>treading on his heels</u> without much effort.</p><p><i>tread on someone’s toes—</i>offend a person by treating him insensitively: As I was mentally formulating responses to it, I also became aware that I should be careful not to <u>tread on his toes</u>.</p> </entry>
